New Records: Senegal secured their place in the knockout stages of AFCON 2023 with a 3-1 victory over Cameroon.
Key Match Events: The match is crucial for both Guinea and Senegal, with Guinea needing just one point to secure qualification and Senegal aiming to finish top of the group.
Pre-Game Insights: Guinea will be determined to avoid complacency to secure qualification, while Senegal will look to maintain their unbeaten run.
Senegal may make changes to their starting lineup due to injuries, with Nicolas Jackson and Iliman Ndiaye potentially featuring from the start.
Guinea's resolute determination to secure qualification could make this a tighter encounter than many predict.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Guinea and Senegal shared the same group at the previous AFCON, playing out a goalless draw.
Guinea's form in all competitions includes a mix of wins, draws, and losses, while Senegal has been unbeaten in their last six matches.
